                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for jianyu &amp;lt;yujian@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/94e11602-472f-11ea-a1c8-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/94e11602-472f-11ea-a1c8-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_112 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
